query: UPDATE briefing_grupo bg SET bg.eventoId = (SELECT e.id FROM eventos e INNER JOIN turmas t ON e.turmaId = t.id WHERE t.codigo = '654' AND e.tipoEvento = 'foto_estudio' ORDER BY e.id LIMIT 1) WHERE bg.eventoId IN (SELECT DISTINCT bf.eventoId FROM briefing_formando bf INNER JOIN formandos f ON bf.formandoId = f.id INNER JOIN turmas t ON f.turmaId = t.id WHERE t.codigo = '654');
